#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.70"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.70:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.70:0.2"
msgid "7. Arahantavagga "
msgstr "7. The Perfected Ones "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 70. Rajanīyasaṇṭhitasutta → rajanīyasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn22.70:0.3"
msgid "70. Rajanīyasaṇṭhitasutta "
msgstr "70. Definitely Arousing "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn22.70:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.70:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha … and asked him, "

msgctxt "sn22.70:1.3"
msgid "“sādhu me, bhante, bhagavā saṃkhittena dhammaṃ desetu, yamahaṃ bhagavato dhammaṃ sutvā … pe … vihareyyan”ti. "
msgstr "“Sir, may the Buddha please teach me Dhamma in brief. When I’ve heard it, I’ll live alone, withdrawn, diligent, keen, and resolute.” "

# NOTE: Not sure why BB has “appears” here. Santhita is fairly rare as a suffix, but it clearly means “established in, firmly fixed in”. Could BB have misread it as sandittha?
#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.70:1.4"
msgid "“Yaṃ kho, bhikkhu, rajanīyasaṇṭhitaṃ; tatra te chando pahātabbo”ti. "
msgstr "“Mendicant, give up desire for anything that’s stuck in what’s arousing.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.70:1.5"
msgid "“Aññātaṃ, bhagavā, aññātaṃ, sugatā”ti. "
msgstr "“Understood, Blessed One! Understood, Holy One!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn22.70:2.1"
msgid "“Yathā kathaṃ pana tvaṃ, bhikkhu, mayā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāsī”ti? "
msgstr "“But how do you see the detailed meaning of my brief statement?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.70:2.2"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ kho, bhante, rajanīyasaṇṭhitaṃ; tatra me chando pahātabbo. "
msgstr "“Sir, form is stuck in what’s arousing; I should give up desire for it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.70:2.3"
msgid "Vedanā … "
msgstr "Feeling … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.70:2.4"
msgid "saññā … "
msgstr "Perception … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.70:2.5"
msgid "saṅkhārā … "
msgstr "Choices … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.70:2.6"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ rajanīyasaṇṭhitaṃ; tatra me chando pahātabbo. "
msgstr "Consciousness is stuck in what’s arousing; I should give up desire for it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.70:2.7"
msgid "Imassa khvāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa evaṃ vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāmī”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how I understand the detailed meaning of the Buddha’s brief statement.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn22.70:3.1"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, bhikkhu. "
msgstr "“Good, good, mendicant! "

msgctxt "sn22.70:3.2"
msgid "Sādhu kho tvaṃ, bhikkhu, mayā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāsi. "
msgstr "It’s good that you understand the detailed meaning of what I’ve said in brief like this. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.70:3.3"
msgid "Rūpaṃ kho, bhikkhu, rajanīyasaṇṭhitaṃ; tatra te chando pahātabbo. "
msgstr "“Form is stuck in what’s arousing; you should give up desire for it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.70:3.4"
msgid "Vedanā … "
msgstr "Feeling … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.70:3.5"
msgid "saññā … "
msgstr "Perception … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.70:3.6"
msgid "saṅkhārā … "
msgstr "Choices … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.70:3.7"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ rajanīyasaṇṭhitaṃ; tatra te chando pahātabbo. "
msgstr "Consciousness is stuck in what’s arousing; you should give up desire for it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.70:3.8"
msgid "Imassa kho, bhikkhu, mayā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa evaṃ vitthārena attho daṭṭhabbo”ti … pe … "
msgstr "This is how to understand the detailed meaning of what I said in brief.” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.70:3.9"
msgid "aññataro ca pana so bhikkhu arahataṃ ahosīti. "
msgstr "And that mendicant became one of the perfected. "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.70:3.10"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

